1. *Trenutak* je zaista značajan za našu porodicu. (This moment is really important for our family.)
2. Osećala je da je *trenutak* ispunjen velikom nadom. (She felt that the moment was filled with great hope.)
3. Svi smo čekali na taj *trenutak*. (We all waited for that moment.)
4. Zahvaljujući njemu, imali smo priliku da se pripremimo za taj *trenutak*. (Thanks to him, we had the chance to prepare for that moment.)
5. Još uvek ne mogu da verujem da se to zaista desilo u tom *trenutku*. (I still can't believe that it really happened at that moment.)